The paper discusses a deep Q-learning algorithm for control, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses stability and convergence issues, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for deep Q-learning, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
